info.description:
The gw20e.forms package provides a powerful
      API form creating and handling electronic forms. The API is
      based on the concepts of XForms, and enables complex forms and
      validation. The gw20e.forms package contains base
      implementations for use with Plone and Pyramid. Django is likely
      to follow soon.
info.name: gw20e.forms
info.summary: Python API for creating and handling forms
info.html_description:
The gw20e.forms package provides a powerful
API form creating and handling electronic forms. The API is based on the concepts of XForms, and enables complex forms and validation. The gw20e.forms package contains base implementations for use with Plone and Pyramid. Django is likely to follow soon.
